\begin{align*} \int_0^{\pi/2}x^n\cos x\,dx&=\left(\frac{\pi}2\right)^n-n\int_0^{\pi/2}x^{n-1}\sin x\,dx\\ &=\left(\frac{\pi}2\right)^n-n(n-1)\int_0^{\pi/2}x^{n-2}\cos x\,dx\;. \end{align*}
